{"tid":633062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"入到一間公司發覺文化麻麻","createTime":"2018-04-18T03:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T14:28:33.000Z","uid":886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c95044a9da7b20d4027d6171c0fb41033d0a8d2f","tid":633062,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"大多都是刷鞋文化<br />\n上級下屬同事都係<br />\n有啲違背公司定政策，同價值觀<br />\n但作為最低級又能做什麼<br />\n相信做了異類下場都係慘<br />\n只能滅聲保平安嗎？<br />\n現實不平則鳴一定是好嗎<br />\n一人力量太小，根本無用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以點?"},{"pid":"e804e7e381b4d021f1a0382a87f8fdde722b273f","tid":633062,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"好想辭工,<br />\n但係岩岩入去做冇耐,<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知點算好<br />\n覺得好唔自在<br />\n好嘔心,我平時都係自己lunch帶飯<br />\n我真係唔想痴佢地咁多...."},{"pid":"f7a51e3c96035760df0ea6e0a9e6f5d313c61220","tid":633062,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"認真討論"},{"pid":"6ba28484bea13cb0a8c2050ce733f967fc28cd53","tid":633062,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"搞女上司"},{"pid":"5dc70500e2ae5440d26056fb6f798079981eac2d","tid":633062,"uid":43412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"走 <br />\n自己唔想學佢地 就走 唔係生存唔到<br />\n<br />\n利串：試過 一個月走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af35048949555aeb8d22a322267c4367b12fbbf","tid":633062,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ba28484bea13cb0a8c2050ce733f967fc28cd53","tid":633062,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"搞女上司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"有冇攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2df6f536bf0107afa58240f970ca69881a49bb","tid":633062,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco